{"word":"βοηθέω","slug":"βοηθέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βοηθέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βοηθός'><el>βοηθός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to come to aid, to succour, assist, aid</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to give aid, come to the rescue</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a> <p/></div>"}]}